title: Regular season average attendance of the Milwaukee Brewers 2009 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Average attendance, containing a total of 11 data points.
In general Average attendance has stayed the same over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2012 and 2013.
The highest Average attendance, of value 37918.0 was reached at Year 2011
The lowest Average attendance, of value 28575.0 was reported at Year 2016
